preference.name: appbar_title_contents
preference.preference_description: Specifies the content of the title string in the application bar for the rich client. Each value must be on its own line. Any other values are rendered as literal text with single space separators after the character. Valid Values: 'user', 'userid', 'group', 'role', 'site', 'curr_proj', 'prev_login_time', 'prev_session_ip', 'current_login_time', 'locationcode', 'version', 'change_notice'
